<p><strong>Last updated:</strong> September 25, 2025</p>

<p>Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how our Hotel Management System (“we,” “our,” or “the system”) collects, uses, and protects the information of our customers, staff, and partners. By using the system, you agree to the practices described in this policy.</p>

<div class="section">
    <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>We may collect the following types of information when you use our system:</p>

    <h3>Personal Information (Guests &amp; Customers):</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>Full name</li>
        <li>Contact details (email, phone number, address)</li>
        <li>Identification details (e.g., passport or CNIC number, if required by law)</li>
        <li>Reservation details (check-in/check-out dates, room preferences)</li>
        <li>Payment information (processed securely through payment gateways)</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Operational Information (Hotels &amp; Staff):</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>Hotel details (name, address, facilities)</li>
        <li>Room details (type, charges, availability)</li>
        <li>Employee/staff details necessary for managing reservations and services</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Technical Information:</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>Log files, device information, IP address</li>
        <li>Browser type and version</li>
        <li>Cookies for session management and user preferences</li>
    </ul>
</div>

<div class="section">
    <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>To process reservations and manage bookings</li>
        <li>To generate invoices and process payments</li>
        <li>To improve customer experience and hotel operations</li>
        <li>To comply with legal or regulatory requirements</li>
        <li>To enhance system security and prevent fraud</li>
    </ul>
</div>

<div class="section">
    <h2>3. Data Sharing &amp; Disclosure</h2>
    <p>We do not sell or rent your personal data. Information may only be shared with:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Hotel staff and administrators responsible for managing reservations</li>
        <li>Third-party payment providers (only for processing payments)</li>
        <li>Law enforcement or government authorities, if legally required</li>
    </ul>
</div>

<div class="section">
    <h2>4. Data Storage &amp; Security</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>All sensitive data is stored securely in our database with encryption where applicable.</li>
        <li>Access to data is restricted to authorized personnel only.</li>
        <li>We regularly update our system to protect against unauthorized access, misuse, or loss.</li>
    </ul>
</div>

<div class="section">
    <h2>5. Data Retention</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Reservation history is retained for business records and audit purposes.</li>
        <li>If you request account deletion, we will anonymize or delete personal data unless retention is required by law.</li>
    </ul>
</div>

<div class="section">
    <h2>6. Your Rights</h2>
    <p>Depending on your jurisdiction (e.g., GDPR in the EU), you may have the right to:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Access your personal data</li>
        <li>Request correction of inaccurate data</li>
        <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
        <li>Restrict or object to certain processing activities</li>
        <li>Request a copy of your data in a portable format</li>
    </ul>
    <p>To exercise your rights, please contact us using the details below.</p>
</div>

<div class="section">
    <h2>7. Cookies &amp; Tracking</h2>
    <p>Our system may use cookies to:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Keep you logged in during your session</li>
        <li>Remember preferences such as language and display settings</li>
        <li>Analyze usage trends to improve performance</li>
    </ul>
    <p>You may disable cookies in your browser settings, but some features may not function properly.</p>
</div>

<div class="section">
    <h2>9. Updates to This Policy</h2>
    <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with a revised “Last Updated” date.</p>
</div>

<div class="section">
    <h2>10. Contact Us</h2>
    <p>If you have questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or how your data is handled, please contact:</p>
    <p>
        <strong>Hotel Management System Admin</strong><br>
        📧 systemadmin@hotelmanagement.com<br>
        📞 +92 300 0000000
    </p>
</div>